  <other_name type="common_name">Charleston sandwort</other_name>
  <discussion>Variety charlestonensis is known from the New York Mountains, Inyo County, California, and adjacent Nevada. It may be more closely allied to Eremogone kingii than to E. congesta.</discussion>
